quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  89,1,"By the dawn,"
  89,2,"and the ten nights,"
  89,3,"and the even and the odd,"
  89,4,"and by the night when it departs."
  89,5,"Is there in this an oath for one endowed with understanding?"{1},footnotes:1:1
  89,6,"Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with Ad"{1},footnotes:1:1
  89,7,"of Iram, known for their lofty columns,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  89,8,"the like of whom no nation was ever created in the lands of the world?"{1},footnotes:1:1
  89,9,"And how did He deal with Thamud who hewed out rocks in the valley?"{1},footnotes:1:1
  89,10,"And with Pharaoh of the tent pegs"{1},footnotes:1:1